subs.text:
@Lift_Our_Voice @Freakonomics It’s horribly troubling for society.

The vast majority of people, in any large group, are honest and well-meaning, or believe they are.

⚠️ The highly-evolved instincts that served our distant hunter-gather ancestors well haven’t had very long to adapt to life in huge societies.

