@Lift_Our_Voice Most humans desire #agency, but many of us either don’t know it is possible or have given up seeking it.

Research has shown that even non-partisan messages such as “4 out of 5 of your neighbors voted in the last election” can be highly motivational! 

*Use only real stats, obvs!

